[[File:2021-08-21_Olaf_Scholz_0309.JPG|thumb]]
2020年8月10日，社民党提名朔尔茨为该党在2021年联邦选举中的德国总理候选人，肖尔茨属于社民党的中间派<ref>{{cite news |title=SPD-Spitze nominiert Olaf Scholz als Kanzlerkandidaten |url=https://www.zeit.de/politik/deutschland/2020-08/olaf-scholz-spd-kanzlerkandidat |access-date=2021-09-26 |archive-date=2020-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820113316/https://www.zeit.de/zustimmung?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zeit.de%2Fpolitik%2Fdeutschland%2F2020-08%2Folaf-scholz-spd-kanzlerkandidat |url-status=live }}</ref>，他的提名被《时代周报》视为标志着社会民主党之左派的衰落。<ref>{{cite news |title=Ende des linken Flügels |url=https://taz.de/Olaf-Scholz-wird-SPD-Kanzlerkandidat/!5706158/|work=Die Tageszeitung|language=de|access-date=2021-09-26 |archive-date=2021-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411100342/https://taz.de/Olaf-Scholz-wird-SPD-Kanzlerkandidat/!5706158/ |url-status=live }}</ref>朔尔茨领导社民党在选举中以微弱优势获胜，赢得了25.8%的选票和联邦议院的206个席位。<ref>{{Cite web|author=Frederik Pleitgen, Salma Abdelaziz, Nadine Schmidt, Stephanie Halasz and Laura Smith-Spark|title=SPD wins most seats in Germany's landmark election, preliminary official results show|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/09/26/europe/germany-election-results-polls-2021-grm-intl/index.html|access-date=2021-09-27|website=CNN|archive-date=2021-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210927040139/https://www.cnn.com/2021/09/26/europe/germany-election-results-polls-2021-grm-intl/index.html|url-status=live}}</ref>这次胜利后，他被广泛认为是最有可能成为德国的下一任[[德国总理|总理]]，并与[[联盟90/绿党|绿党]]和[[自由民主党_(德国)|自由民主党]]组成[[联合政府|联合政府]]。<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|date=2021-10-15|title=Die Ampel kann kommen: SPD, FDP und Grüne empfehlen Koalitionsgespräche|language=de|work=Der Spiegel|url=https://www.spiegel.de/politik/deutschland/spd-fdp-und-gruene-empfehlen-koalitionsgespraeche-a-e8617bfc-869f-4dc6-9a31-b295589a17b0|access-date=2021-10-15|issn=2195-1349|archive-date=2021-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211015143513/https://www.spiegel.de/politik/deutschland/spd-fdp-und-gruene-empfehlen-koalitionsgespraeche-a-e8617bfc-869f-4dc6-9a31-b295589a17b0|url-status=live}}</ref>11月24日，社民党、绿党和联邦民主党达成了联合协议，由朔尔茨担任德国新总理。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Apetz|first=Andreas|date=2021-11-24|title=Ampel-Koalition: So sieht der Fahrplan nach dem Koalitionsvertrag aus|url=https://www.fr.de/politik/ampel-koalition-koalitionsvertrag-so-geht-es-weiter-spd-fdp-gruene-regierung-91137643.html|url-status=no|access-date=2021-12-08|website=Frankfurter Rundschau|language=de|archive-date=2021-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211208150012/https://www.fr.de/politik/ampel-koalition-koalitionsvertrag-so-geht-es-weiter-spd-fdp-gruene-regierung-91137643.html}}</ref>

2022年5月8日，朔尔茨發表講話，表示德国曾犯下反人类罪行，並且德国永远不会再进行战争，不会再讓种族灭绝發生。<ref>{{cite news |title=日媒关注朔尔茨承认“德国曾犯反人类罪行”，誓言“永不再战”，日网民：日德领导人“格局有差距” 来源：环球网作者：林泽宇  2022-05-09 12:34 |url=https://world.huanqiu.com/article/47w6Vg4HL64 |accessdate=2022-05-09 |archive-date=2022-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220611044550/https://world.huanqiu.com/article/47w6Vg4HL64 }}</ref>

== 政治立場 ==
蕭茲被認為是社民黨中的溫和派<ref>{{cite news |last1=Chazan |first1=Guy |title=Olaf Scholz, a sound guardian for Germany's finances |url=https://www.ft.com/content/170b9d0a-0cc2-11e8-8eb7-42f857ea9f09 |website=Financial Times |access-date=7 September 2021 |date=9 February 2018 |archive-date=26 August 2021 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210826204338/https://www.ft.com/content/170b9d0a-0cc2-11e8-8eb7-42f857ea9f09 |url-status=live }}</ref>。 由於他的說話風格被人認為比較乏味，被媒體稱為「機器人蕭茲」（{{lang-de|Scholzomat}}）<ref>Brost, M., & P. Dausend: [http://www.zeit.de/2013/26/olaf-scholz-scholzomat ''Olaf Scholz: Ich war der „Scholzomat“.''] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211027161612/https://www.zeit.de/2013/26/olaf-scholz-scholzomat |date=27 October 2021 }} In: ''Zeit 26/2013''.</ref><ref>[https://www.zeit.de/politik/deutschland/2021-09/olaf-scholz-the-discreet-charm-of-the-scholzomat?utm_referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2F The discreet charm of the Scholzomat] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211025205251/https://www.zeit.de/politik/deutschland/2021-09/olaf-scholz-the-discreet-charm-of-the-scholzomat?utm_referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2F |date=25 October 2021 }} In: ''Zeit'', 26 September 2021.</ref>。
=== 環保與氣候議題 ===
蕭茲主張擴大投資可再生能源以取代化石燃料。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Bloomberg - Are you a robot?|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=0b92e42b-93e4-11ec-93f2-4b504b794c61&url=L25ld3MvYXJ0aWNsZXMvMjAyMS0xMC0xMy9zY2hvbHotc2F5cy1uZXctZ292ZXJubWVudC13aWxsLW1ha2UtcmVuZXdhYmxlLWVuZXJneS1wdXNo|access-date=2022-02-22|work=www.bloomberg.com|archive-date=2022-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220222135237/https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=0b92e42b-93e4-11ec-93f2-4b504b794c61&url=L25ld3MvYXJ0aWNsZXMvMjAyMS0xMC0xMy9zY2hvbHotc2F5cy1uZXctZ292ZXJubWVudC13aWxsLW1ha2UtcmVuZXdhYmxlLWVuZXJneS1wdXNo|dead-url=no}}</ref>2021年5月，蕭茲主張建立一個關於氣候的國際組織，並且討論出全球各國對於減碳的最低目標。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Gemeinsame Ziele und Standards: Scholz will internationalen Klimaclub gründen|url=https://www.rnd.de/politik/scholz-will-internationalen-klimaclub-gruenden-fuer-gemeinsame-ziele-und-standards-IERK4CQ6ZNCY7AYOG3RU3C4A6Y.html|access-date=2022-02-22|work=www.rnd.de|language=de|archive-date=2021-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211025211540/https://www.rnd.de/politik/scholz-will-internationalen-klimaclub-gruenden-fuer-gemeinsame-ziele-und-standards-IERK4CQ6ZNCY7AYOG3RU3C4A6Y.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在聯合政府的白皮書中，以蕭茲為首的新聯合政府同意要在2030年以前，完全禁止燃煤發電。這比德國原先的計劃提前8年。除此之外，德國計劃在2040年前完全禁止天然氣發電。同時新政府也將配合歐洲理事會的決議，在2035年完全禁止內燃機汽車的銷售。<ref>{{Cite news|title=EXCLUSIVE German parties agree on 2030 coal phase-out in coalition talks -sources|url=https://www.reuters.com/business/cop/exclusive-germanys-government-in-waiting-agrees-phase-out-coal-by-2030-sources-2021-11-23/|newspaper=Reuters|date=2021-11-23|accessdate=2022-02-22|language=en|first=Markus|last=Wacket|archive-date=2022-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220303202425/https://www.reuters.com/business/cop/exclusive-germanys-government-in-waiting-agrees-phase-out-coal-by-2030-sources-2021-11-23/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 強制疫苗令 ===
在2021的國會選舉期間，蕭茲曾提案要推出全國的強制新冠肺炎疫苗接種令。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Germany's Scholz urges compulsory COVID-19 jabs for all adults|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-germany-politics-scholz-mandatory-vac-idUSKBN2JM1HS|newspaper=Reuters|date=2022-01-12|accessdate=2022-02-22|language=en|archive-date=2022-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220326040821/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-germany-politics-scholz-mandatory-vac-idUSKBN2JM1HS|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2022年一月，在一場聯邦議會的演講中，蕭茲再次重申他對成人強制疫苗接種令的支持，並表示新冠肺炎不會神奇地消失。他表示，如果沒有強制接種令，德國將無法進入後疫情時代。<ref>{{Cite web|title=German Chancellor Olaf Scholz eyes COVID vaccine mandate {{!}} DW {{!}} 23.01.2022|url=https://www.dw.com/en/german-chancellor-olaf-scholz-eyes-covid-vaccine-mandate/a-60531098|access-date=2022-02-22|last=Welle (www.dw.com)|first=Deutsche|work=DW.COM|language=en-GB|archive-date=2022-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220417003617/https://www.dw.com/en/german-chancellor-olaf-scholz-eyes-covid-vaccine-mandate/a-60531098|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 與美國的關係 ===
蕭茲將美國稱作「歐洲最親密與最重要的夥伴」。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Washington Hopeful of Close Relations With Germany’s Scholz|url=https://www.voanews.com/a/washington-hopeful-of-close-relations-with-germany-scholz/6343014.html|access-date=2022-02-22|work=VOA|language=en|archive-date=2022-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220326040822/https://www.voanews.com/a/washington-hopeful-of-close-relations-with-germany-scholz/6343014.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在2019年12月，蕭茲批評美國對北溪二號的制裁，認為「此舉是對歐洲的內政與主權的嚴重干涉。」<ref>{{Cite news|title='We firmly reject this': Germany rebukes US over sanctions on critical gas pipeline|url=https://www.abc.net.au/news/2019-12-22/germany-hits-back-at-us-donald-trump-sanctions-on-nord-stream-2/11821624|newspaper=ABC News|date=2019-12-21|accessdate=2022-02-22|language=en-AU|archive-date=2022-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220326132219/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2019-12-22/germany-hits-back-at-us-donald-trump-sanctions-on-nord-stream-2/11821624|dead-url=no}}</ref>

就核武議題，蕭茲支持美軍在德國境內部署核子武器。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Incoming German government commits to NATO nuclear deterrent|url=https://www.defensenews.com/global/europe/2021/11/24/incoming-german-government-commits-to-nato-nuclear-deterrent/|access-date=2022-02-22|date=2021-11-24|last=Sprenger|first=Sebastian|work=Defense News|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220423202153/https://www.defensenews.com/global/europe/2021/11/24/incoming-german-government-commits-to-nato-nuclear-deterrent/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在2022年1月，紐約時報報導，美國和北約盟友對於德國對俄羅斯的態度表達憂心，認為德國無法在[[2021年－2022年俄乌危机|2021年－2022年俄乌危机]]中，對俄羅斯表達強硬態度。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Where Is Germany in the Ukraine Standoff? Its Allies Wonder.|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2022/01/25/world/europe/germany-russia-nato-ukraine.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2022-01-25|accessdate=2022-02-22|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Katrin|last=Bennhold|archive-date=2022-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220413180202/https://www.nytimes.com/2022/01/25/world/europe/germany-russia-nato-ukraine.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 蕭茲的政府原本拒絕向烏克蘭提供武器，然而，在[[2022年俄羅斯入侵烏克蘭|俄羅斯入侵烏克蘭]]後，蕭茲改變政策，並向烏克蘭提供反坦克武器和刺針導彈。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Russia Ukraine news Live: Russian troops enter Kharkiv city as fight resumes|url=https://www.marca.com/en/lifestyle/world-news/2022/02/26/6219f7f146163fe5598b45fe.html|access-date=2022-03-02|date=2022-02-26|work=MARCA|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220422225531/https://www.marca.com/en/lifestyle/world-news/2022/02/26/6219f7f146163fe5598b45fe.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

